{
  "stem": "11179.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, as you-- you know, historically or whatever, that was a time, the early '30s was a time, when electrical appliances, electric equipment was really going into high gear.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Motors, everything, you know-- it-- it-- it had a tremendous future.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He worked for a short time for a private paper, which was a-- a-- a kind of a steel-- similar, in the steel industry, but it was a small, Jewish owned paper.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after a year or so, that man folded up, too-- the owner of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naturally, the Nazis did everything to pressure papers like this out-- out of business.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was-- if he didn't close, he got very small, so there was-- there was nothing there anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then my father worked for-- for three years for the-- as a volunteer, because they don't give you a job, as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you-- if you-- you know, if you-- a job was-- another job to get was almost impossible under the circumstances.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he worked for-- for three years at the voluntary for the Jewish community council.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Youth and Welfare Office, they called that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a branch office in our neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he got lunch there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Meanwhile, my grandmother had passed away, and she had a large apartment house in Frankfurt-- the house I was born in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was enough income, and mother's two brothers decided in-- that they pay us from the profit of the house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It-- it was, of course, mortgaged somewhat, by that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Originally, it was owned clear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they paid us enough so we can make a living, and take it off at the end, when they would sell it, for what my mother-- my mother's share would have been.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
